are doing the digging

00:24:35.350 --> 00:24:38.160
but it actually runs under
a Palestinian neighborhood

00:24:38.160 --> 00:24:40.250
and that's causing
their houses to collapse

00:24:40.250 --> 00:24:43.640
and there's tremendous
tension around this site.

00:24:43.640 --> 00:24:46.800
And it just reminds
you that the battles

00:24:46.800 --> 00:24:50.240
that David fought are
still going on.

00:24:50.240 --> 00:24:53.730
So I've only got a few minutes
left and I want to leave time

00:24:53.730 --> 00:24:56.950
for questions so I'm just
going to go quickly to say

00:24:56.950 --> 00:25:02.550
that my baby harpist grew
up to be a big harpist.

00:25:02.550 --> 00:25:04.430
See, I warned you there
would be family photos.

00:25:04.430 --> 00:25:09.840
And on the way, he was having
his Bar Mitzvah and because

00:25:09.840 --> 00:25:13.350 position:56%
of the connection with David and the
harp, he decided to play his harp

00:25:13.350 --> 00:25:19.200
at his Bar Mitzvah, and he chose
to play a beautiful arrangement

00:25:19.200 --> 00:25:22.410
of Leonard Cohen's
wonderful song Hallelujah.

00:25:22.410 --> 00:25:25.170
And so I not only owe him
the idea for the book,

00:25:25.170 --> 00:25:28.650
I also owe him the title because
the first line of that song

00:25:28.650 --> 00:25:31.700
of course is, they say
there was a secret chord

00:25:31.700 --> 00:25:34.670
that David played and
it pleased the lord.

00:25:34.670 --> 00:25:40.290 position:56%
But it's the seldom sung later verse
that I think really sums up David,

00:25:40.290 --> 00:25:45.770
the verse that goes, there's a
blaze of light in every word,

00:25:45.770 --> 00:25:50.400
it doesn't matter which you heard,
the holy or the broken, Hallelujah.

00:25:50.400 --> 00:25:56.260
And David is holy and broken, and
I think we all are to some extent,

00:25:56.260 --> 00:26:01.380
and I think that that geniality and
that complexity is what makes him

00:26:01.380 --> 00:26:05.280
such a fascinating figure and
keeps drawing us back to him.

00:26:05.280 --> 00:26:07.080
