be plausible and truth needn't be.

00:27:34.210 --> 00:27:37.830
So I'm always looking for those
implausible truths like the fact

00:27:37.830 --> 00:27:42.110
that a village quarantined itself
voluntarily during the plague

00:27:42.110 --> 00:27:45.660
