Greek and graduated Harvard in 1665.

00:27:50.490 --> 00:27:54.820
If I made them up it wouldn't
be so exciting and the fact is

00:27:54.820 --> 00:27:59.230
that those things happened, but
then the second thing I need is

00:27:59.230 --> 00:28:02.280
that there not be too
much known about them

00:28:02.280 --> 00:28:07.150 position:56%
because if Caleb the Native American
had kept a journal of his time

00:28:07.150 --> 00:28:09.850
at Harvard, there would be
no space for me and it's

00:28:09.850 --> 00:28:13.620 position:56%
because we don't know much about his
experience, the only way to engage

00:28:13.620 --> 00:28:16.950
with it is through imagination.

00:28:16.950 --> 00:28:22.940
So, I need the void as well as
the skeleton of intriguing facts,

00:28:22.940 --> 00:28:24.250
